        "title": "Linux packaging retry and changelog tooling improvements",
        "summary": "Release Infrastructure: Linux AppRun download failures now also trigger an automatic retry, and nightly changelog validation was relaxed to reduce false-positive failures.",
        "items": [
          {
            "text": "Linux AppImage builds now retry automatically when the AppRun binary download returns a 5xx error, complementing the earlier macOS DMG retry logic and making desktop packaging more resilient on both platforms.",
